**Purpose:** Sealed entity boundary. Mot[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] entity (persona, cell, governance object) co[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] 1 `.anc` = identity neo bat[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] bien[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME].

