**Purpose:** Sealed persona memory snapshot. `.kris` la[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] format legacy, `.na` la[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] v1.2 R01 (active migration).

**Pattern:** `<entity>khuong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME]<semver>.kris` (legacy) → `<entity>khuong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME]<semver>.na` (v1.2)

